      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1399 - The Prophet (sw) said in his advice to Imam Ali (as): \"O’ Ali, adhere to the night prayer, adhere to the night prayer, adhere to the night prayer”."
